content: I was running a workflow which involved intake-esm, dask, and xpersist and ran into an AttributeError: 'HighLevelGraph' object has no attribute '_dask_distributed_pack_' error... has anyone seen this before?
I think this is related to a version incompatibility

I have been using the following package versions:

  • bokeh==1.4
  • dask==2.14
  • distributed==2.14
  • dask-jobqueue==0.7.1

I've tried relaxing the pinned versions, but haven't found a working alternative.
